This paper focuses on the development of a fully autonomous small rotorcraft UAS for long-term observation missions, which involves the integration of various technologies such as computer vision, machine learning, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is Robotics (cs.RO), followed by Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also addresses emergency response and energy replenishment, which are related to Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Multi-Agent Systems (cs.MA), respectively.
